flowchart LR
    A[Raw IDB/UDB or legacy NPZ] --> B[calwidget_v2_analysis.py]
    B --> C[ScanAnalysis]
    B --> D[DelaySolution]

    D --> E[kept_band_mask]
    D --> F[residual_kept_band_mask]
    D --> G[relative_ns]
    D --> H[manual antenna overrides]

    C --> I[calwidget_v2_plots.py]
    D --> I

    I --> J[Sum Amp]
    I --> K[Sum Pha]
    I --> L[Inband Fit]
    I --> M[Relative Phase plus Fit]
    I --> N[Per-Band Residual Phase]
    I --> O[Residual Delay Per Band]
    I --> P[Daily NPZ export entry]

    C --> Q[calwidget_v2_api.py]
    D --> Q
    I --> Q

    Q --> R[overview-data]
    Q --> S[heatmap-data]
    Q --> T[time-history]
    Q --> U[update and apply endpoints]

    R --> V[calwidget_v2_frontend/app.js]
    S --> V
    T --> V
    U --> V

    V --> W[Interactive browser workflow]
    W --> X[Sidecar persistence]
    W --> Y[SQL save]
    W --> Z[Daily NPZ save]
